## Internal-only Lab Setup
#
# If this is entirely internal and you do not want
# Let’s Encrypt/public certs yet:
#
# {
#     email admin@example.com
# }
#
# llm.internal.example.com {
#
#     tls internal
#
#     encode zstd gzip
#
#     reverse_proxy litellm:4000
# }
# That creates an internal CA-signed cert.
#
# Clients will need to trust the Caddy internal CA
# certificate or they will see TLS warnings.
#
## Simple test-only setup
#
# For quick LAN testing without HTTPS
#
# :80 {
#     reverse_proxy litellm:4000
# }

:80 {
    reverse_proxy litellm:4000
}